  "statement": {
    "markdown": "Given a sorted doubly linked list, remove duplicates from the list and return the head of the modified list. The list is sorted in ascending order and each node has a unique identifier. The input list is guaranteed to be non-empty and the nodes are guaranteed to have unique values. The output should be the head of the modified list with duplicates removed.",
